  STATE_GOVT: "Step 1: Visit kpsc.kar.nic.in for the official notification\nStep 2: Register on the KPSC portal with your Aadhaar and mobile\nStep 3: Fill the online application form with all required details\nStep 4: Upload required documents: photo, signature, certificates\nStep 5: Pay application fee online (₹200 General, ₹100 SC/ST)\nStep 6: Download acknowledgment receipt for reference\nStep 7: Appear for written examination as per hall ticket\nStep 8: Qualify written exam for physical test / interview (if applicable)\nStep 9: Attend document verification and medical examination",
